quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,103,"Nambo ŵatiukajepepale n’dingo wao (wa yambone, ni kusitopa yakusakala), basi ŵanganyao ni aŵala ŵalipelelwekasyisye achimisyene, takaŵe ŵandamo mu Jahannama."
  23,104,"Moto tiukachome ngope syao soni ŵanyao mwalakwemo takaŵe chechena! (Aku sili sipotweche ngomo syao lugomo lwakwinani gunda chilikati chantwe, lwapasi gunda nchisou)."
  23,105,"(Takawusyidweje kuti): “Ana ma Ȃya Gangu nganigasoomedwaga kukwenu, basi jenumanja ni mwaliji nkugakanila?”"
  25,49,"Kuti ni galakwego tusyuchisye chilambo chachiwe, ni tumwechesye ine (mu iwumbe) yatwaigumbile (mpela) ilango kwisa soni ŵandu ŵajinji."
  25,50,"Soni chisimu Uwwe tukujigaŵanyaga (wulajo) chilikati chao kuti aŵeje ŵakumbuchila (ukoto Wetu), nambo ŵandu ŵajinji akukana (chikulupi) ikaŵeje ukafili (basi)."
  25,51,"Soni tungasache tungatumisye m’musi uliose nkutetela (jwaojwaope)."
  26,22,"“Ana soni weleu ni ukoto wakungumba nao kutendaga mwaŵisile mu ukapolo ŵanache ŵa Israila!”"
  26,23,"Firiauna jwatite: “Ana M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosopejo ni nduni?”"
  26,24,"(Musa) jwatite: “M’mbuje jwa kumawunde ni petaka ni yaili chilikati chakwe, nam’baga jenumanja nkwete ntima wakusaka kusimichisya (tinsimichisye yele).”"